ESSENTIAL TRAVEL APP FOR COLLEGE STUDENTS: affordable and easy way to make your trip to college more comfortable and fun

• Share your ride to college with fellow peers

• Find people within your college willing to share a ride to college by making a generous contribution

• Make new friends on the trip to college

OFFER A RIDE:
• Publish your ride

• Enjoy your ride to college with your fellow peers and share the driving costs

FIND A RIDE:
• Search for students offering a ride to your college

• Get in touch with those students

• Just sit and enjoy the ride